1 4. The Division may adopt regulations necessary to establish and administer
2 the program established pursuant to this section.
3 5. As used in this section, “limited English proficiency” means a person
4 who reads, writes or speaks a language other than English and who cannot
5 readily understand or communicate in the English language in written or spoken
